According to Hartbeespoort Emergency Rescue, about 200 people were on board when the boat caught fire. One person is believed to have burnt to death inside the bathroom, while three drowned after jumping into the water.An eyewitness told eNCA that they spotted smoke coming from the rear of the cruiser. Once flames started erupting at the back, people started screaming and running to the front of the boat.Smaller private crafts in the area headed to the party boat, helping a number of passengers escape the boat. The cause of the fire is still unknown.